      <title>咏昙</title>
      <link>https://iliu.org/3262.html</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Sep 2020 12:15:07 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://iliu.org/3262.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  白如雪，洁似梅
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  欲视昙，必有耐
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  开如白鹭般净洁
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  收如少女般含蓄
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  窗前花苞且难寻
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  开时既是枯萎始
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  若使花儿记心上
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;text-align: center;&#34;&gt;
  花开时分想真谛
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;aligncenter size-full wp-image-3260&#34; src=&#34;https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; width=&#34;850&#34; height=&#34;1001&#34; srcset=&#34;https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7.jpg 850w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7-255x300.jpg 255w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7-768x904.jpg 768w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;">
  白如雪，洁似梅
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  欲视昙，必有耐
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  开如白鹭般净洁
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  收如少女般含蓄
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  窗前花苞且难寻
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  开时既是枯萎始
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  若使花儿记心上
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  花开时分想真谛
</p>
<p><a href="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-3260" src="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7.jpg" alt="" width="850" height="1001" srcset="https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7.jpg 850w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7-255x300.jpg 255w, https://tunan.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/8ec1fbfecf0c7c7-768x904.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  其二
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  寂寞昙花深夜开
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  洁白无瑕人未见
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  一朝凋谢人不知
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  笑问此花何时开
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  白鹭一现不容看
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  就似昙华寿命短
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  幽香缕缕人难闻
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  淡淡清香胜桂兰
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  如若白鹭人易赏
</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
  琼花何苦晚间开
</p>
]]></content:encoded>
